<h1>Password reset</h1>

<p>If you recently requested to reset your talksome password, click the link below:</p>

<%= link_to "Reset password", edit_password_reset_url(@user.reset_token, email: @user.email) %>

<p>The link will expire in two hours.</p>

<p>If you did not request your password to be reset, don't do anything.</p>

<p>Thank you for using talksome!</p>